      {
        "title": "Early Beginnings of Captivity",
        "introduction": "The warnings of the prophets that Israel would fall into Assyrian captivity are already starting to come true. It will be several more years before total collapse takes place, but the record indicates that even now, during Pekah's reign, many of the people of Reuben, Gad, and Manasseh are taken captive by Tiglath-Pileser (King Pul)."
      },
      {
